{"type": "article", "id": 37649, "title": "在这个篮球场上打球，就像掉进了虚拟空间｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-09T23:00:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32586, "name": "yuue Design"}, {"id": 37517, "name": "Peg and Awl Built"}, {"id": 8451, "name": "李奥贝纳"}, {"id": 37518, "name": "Gue"}, {"id": 37519, "name": "Jay DeMerit"}, {"id": 37520, "name": "Ann Carrington"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 205, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170209224517HidfyI4MP3L7jcVU.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Playground by Gue</h3><p>作为城市复兴以及 Carlo Carrà 公园再开发计划的一部分，意大利亚历山德里亚（Alessandria）市政府委托来自西西里岛的壁画家 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gummygue/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gue</a> 以公园内的一座篮球场为画布进行了创作。在保证固有场地划分不变的基础上，Gue 加入了橙、黄、蓝、白四色填充的各类不规则的图形，看上去随性活泼。从俯瞰图来看，在这样的球场上进行比赛似乎像是掉入了虚拟空间一样，加深了动感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224628QemCEXOhxUNqL4cM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224629QF4s17E5tdlfm9ky.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224628D9xl1HcBjVdWzyvY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224629Ff304HQPqx65MYIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702092246294JvmCLQloZNOPqK9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Marlowe Lunch Bag by Peg and Awl Built</h3><p>随着越来越多的消费者和商家开始注重环保，捧着装得满满的牛皮纸袋走在街上的场景就变得不那么常见了。为了保留这一经典的袋子形象，美国的夫妻档手工制品工作室 <a href=\"https://pegandawlbuilt.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peg and Awl Built</a> 选用结实的上蜡帆布制作了这款名为 Marlowe Lunch Bag 帆布购物袋。它连顶部都保留了牛皮纸袋的锯齿状边缘，有着相当高的还原度。这是它的<a href=\"https://pegandawlbuilt.com/collections/bags-1/products/the-marlowe-lunchbag\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 44 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702092246476txc4Ij3XMAKEshJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523810\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224647cwn9Rk45hmHOVYXu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224647sQUJY1Ed02wIp4o8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224648qTsPwVHbt9dGuLFl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.988889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224648mv1kZsbGKWCeiwOo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rockit Log by Jay DeMerit</h3><p>在成为职业足球运动员之前，美国球员 Jay DeMerit 最初选择的道路是工业设计。最近他就以原木废料为素材，设计了这款名为 Rockit Log 的木质无线音响。和其他对废料进行再利用使它们获得新生的设计师一样，DeMerit 希望借此呼吁人们一起保护树木。这些音响都采用手工制作，最大限度地呈现了树木的年轮，因此每一个的造型都是独一无二的。它的顶部配备了便于携带的把手，锂电池充满后可以连续播放 10 小时。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1185030532/rockit-logs-by-usmnt-player-and-product-designer-j\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 199 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224709cFozOSKx13NGVpEq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224706DbcJZWnhyA5zUYou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224707qHuxzyCbnfKPptB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.889706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702092247061Bb7LFuaIZkivXfE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.963235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224707GDTXUSnPHlEZ0mtf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bento by yuue design</h3><p>还记得那个让人误以为自己失手拉坏吊灯的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32005.html\">互动灯具</a>吗？负责设计的 <a href=\"http://www.yuuedesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">yuue design</a> 工作室最近又带来了一款加入互动元素的灯饰 Bento，正如名字所指的那样，在尚未打开的情况下它就像是一个便当盒，只有拉动顶部的提绳，才会露出可以用来放置小物的收纳空间和能够通过灯柱随意调节高度的灯泡。和让人虚惊一场的吊灯不同，两用且身材小巧的 Bento 似乎更实用一些，很适合当作床头灯使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224734PnZlTKO7ape14VC5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224734DGh85qNxJpcIQEOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224734d8Ze3JKWCSPV7QGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224735zQvLXgl6A9MjqId1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224736kyHVxYDXf0S1KCwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Perfect Match by Leo Burnett Design</h3><p>除了蜡烛之外，生活中还有不少需要用到火柴的场合。为了让所有人都能找到那根“perfect match”，李奥贝纳加拿大旗下的<a href=\"http://www.leoburnettdesign.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计部门</a>打造了四种尺寸的火柴以及能将它们全部收纳在一起的火柴盒，火柴盒正面的火柴颜色和大小刚好和纸抽屉中的实物一一对应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224820jqC9wpJmgx1MTX3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224819Vy1z9E6TbQe8pAWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224820TyNALH0OxikjuUg4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224819HcApX92RlFGdqObe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224819ylH6XkSdYZLxiD8s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bouquets and Butterflies by Ann Carrington</h3><p>刀、叉和勺子，这些金属制品在我们的印象中似乎只出现在厨房和餐桌。因此当你看到这套由英国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.anncarrington.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ann Carrington</a> 创作的雕塑 Bouquets and Butterflies 时，或许会因为它们错综复杂的外观一时难分真假，怀疑这是不是将植物镀银的结果。Carrington 以插花的方式将冷冰冰的餐具转化成了栩栩如生的花瓣和根茎，营造出一种有些奇特的生活气息。如果你对 Carrington 的作品感兴趣的话，还可以关注她的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/anncarringtonart/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 和 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AnnCarringtonArtist/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224609VIL0ewUX2tsbWBYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224610KoGYuw8MmgA0LqVi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224610EcOgZf83pMQK6Vt4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224610yrY8Cd3OvIlFfExU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224610EFUq1ztshvLIHuTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170209224609GV0Q1uPc6R9jm5o7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}